com.microsoft.azure.management.sql

Interface SqlDatabase

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChildResource<SqlServer>, ExternalChildResource<SqlDatabase,SqlServer>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.implementation.DatabaseInner>, HasName, HasParent<SqlServer>, HasResourceGroup, Indexable, Refreshable<SqlDatabase>, Updatable<SqlDatabase.Update>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SqlWarehouse

    @Beta(value=V1_7_0)
public interface SqlDatabase
extends ExternalChildResource<SqlDatabase,SqlServer>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.implementation.DatabaseInner>, HasResourceGroup, Refreshable<SqlDatabase>, Updatable<SqlDatabase.Update>
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure SQL Server Database.
